{"title_page": "Andr\u00e9 Cognard", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2011}}\n{{Expand French|Andr\u00e9 Cognard|date=October 2012|topic=sport}}\n'''Andr\u00e9 Cognard''' 8th [[Dan (rank)|dan]], [[shihan]], is the current head of [[Kobayashi aikido]] since the death of its founder [[Hirokazu Kobayashi (aikidoka)]].<ref>{{in lang|fr}} [http://www.3aikido.org Acad\u00e9mie Autonome d'Aikido Kobayashi Hirokazu]</ref><ref>{{in lang|fr}} [http://www.aikido-kobayashi.org/ Kokusai Aikido Kenshukai Kobayashi Hirokazu Ryu Ha]</ref> He has published several books on martial arts in French language.\n\n==Published works==\n*Andre Cognard: ''Le corps conscient''  Dervy, 1999, {{ISBN|2-84454-016-3}}\n*Andre Cognard: ''Civilisation et arts martiaux, ou, Le noeud de la ceinture''  Albin Michel Publications, France, 2000, {{ISBN|2-226-07993-9}}\n*Andre Cognard: ''Le disciple'', Dervy, 2002 {{ISBN|2-84454-150-X}} \n*Andre Cognard: ''Le corps philosophe'', Centon, 2003 {{ISBN|2-915384-00-2}}\n*Andre Cognard: ''L'esprit des arts martiaux''  Albin Michel Publications, France, 2003, {{ISBN|2-226-13684-3}}\n*Andre Cognard: ''Le ma\u00eetre'', Dervy, 2004 {{ISBN|2-84454-283-2}}\n*Andre Cognard: ''Vivre sans ennemi'', Le Reli\u00e9, 2004 {{ISBN|2-914916-44-2}}\n*Andre Cognard: ''Petit manuel d'aikido'', Centon, 2005 {{ISBN|2-915384-01-0}}\n*Andre Cognard: ''M\u00e9moires d'outre-moi'', Centon, 2006 {{ISBN|2-915384-04-5}}\n*Nadja Maria Acioly-R\u00e9gnier, Cl\u00e9mentine Amouroux, Jean Jacques Boutaud, Paul Castella, Patrick Chignol, Andr\u00e9 Cognard, Andrea Debiasi, Marco Favretti, Victor Gouttebroze, Sergio Morra, Giangiorgio Pasqualotto, Jean Claude R\u00e9gnier, Shingai Tanaka: ''Pour qu'\u00e9duquer ne soit pas un monologue'', 2008 {{ISBN|978-2-915384-07-9}}\n*Andre Cognard: ''Lhassa, Osaka, Essendil\u00e8ne'', Centon, 2010 {{ISBN|978-2-915384-08-6}}\n*Andre Cognard: ''La disciple et les sabres invincibles'', Centon, 2012 {{ISBN|978-2-915384-17-8}}\n*Andre Cognard: ''P\u00e8re, Fils'', Centon, 2012 {{ISBN|978-2-915384-10-9}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{in lang|fr}}  [https://web.archive.org/web/20120826121321/http://www.3aikido.org/lecture/andre-cognard-livres Livres \u00e9crits par Andr\u00e9 Cognard]\n*{{in lang|fr}}  [http://theses.univ-lyon2.fr/documents/lyon2/2007/chignol_p#p=0&a=top Th\u00e8se de Patrick Chignol en Sciences de l'\u00e9ducation sur l'influence de la pratique de l\u2019Aikido sur le d\u00e9veloppement du sujet]\n*{{in lang|fr}}  [http://www.aikidojournal.eu/Entretiens/Cognard_Andre_Bourg_Agental/ Interview avec Andr\u00e9 Cognard]\n*{{in lang|fr}}  [https://archive.is/20130701104218/http://eu.aikidojournal.eu/Essai/Andre_Cognard/ Les points de vue d'Andr\u00e9 Cognard]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Cognard, Andre}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:French aikidoka]]\n[[Category:French male writers]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n\n\n{{aikido-bio-stub}}\n{{France-sport-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2011}}\n{{Expand French|Andr\u00e9 Cognard|date=October 2012|topic=sport}}\n'''Andr\u00e9 Cognard''' 8th [[Dan (rank)|dan]], [[shihan]], is the current head of [[Kobayashi aikido]] since the death of its founder [[Hirokazu Kobayashi (aikidoka)]].<ref>{{in lang|fr}} [http://www.3aikido.org Acad\u00e9mie Autonome d'Aikido Kobayashi Hirokazu]</ref><ref>{{in lang|fr}} [http://www.aikido-kobayashi.org/ Kokusai Aikido Kenshukai Kobayashi Hirokazu Ryu Ha]</ref> He has published several books on martial arts in French language.\n\n==Published works==\n*Andre Cognard: ''Le corps conscient''  Dervy, 1999, {{ISBN|2-84454-016-3}}\n*Andre Cognard: ''Civilisation et arts martiaux, ou, Le noeud de la ceinture''  Albin Michel Publications, France, 2000, {{ISBN|2-226-07993-9}}\n*Andre Cognard: ''Le disciple'', Dervy, 2002 {{ISBN|2-84454-150-X}} \n*Andre Cognard: ''Le corps philosophe'', Centon, 2003 {{ISBN|2-915384-00-2}}\n*Andre Cognard: ''L'esp