ifov]]|AZE|2016 Summer}}<br />'''W''' 3\u20131 <sup>PP</sup>\n|colspan=2 {{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Selim Ya\u015far|Ya\u015far]]|TUR|2016 Summer}}<br />'''W''' 3\u20130 <sup>PO</sup>\n|{{gold01}}\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Anzor Boltukayev]]\n|align=left|[[Wrestling at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's freestyle 97 kg|\u221297 kg]]\n|{{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Valerii Andriitsev|Andriitsev]]|UKR|2016 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 1\u20133 <sup>PP</sup>\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|11\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Bilyal Makhov]]\n|align=left|[[Wrestling at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's freestyle 125 kg|\u2212125 kg]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Alen Zasyeyev|Zasyeyev]]|UKR|2016 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 1\u20133 <sup>PP</sup>\n|colspan=6|Did not advance\n|13\n|}\n\n;Men's Greco-Roman\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n!rowspan=2|Athlete\n!rowspan=2|Event\n!Qualification\n!Round of 16\n!Quarterfinal\n!Semifinal\n!Repechage 1\n!Repechage 2\n!colspan=3|Final / {{abbr|BM|Bronze medal match}}\n|-style=\"font-size: 95%\"\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Rank\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Ibragim Labazanov]]\n|align=left|[[Wrestling at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's Greco-Roman 59 kg|\u221259 kg]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Almat Kebispayev|Kebispayev]]|KAZ|2016 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 0\u20133 <sup>PO</sup>\n|colspan=6|Did not advance\n|16\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Islambek Albiev]]\n|align=left|[[Wrestling at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's Greco-Roman 66 kg|\u221266 kg]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Ion Panait|Panait]]|ROU|2016 Summer}}<br />'''W''' 3\u20131 <sup>PP</sup>\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Rasul Chunayev|Chunayev]]|AZE|2016 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 1\u20133 <sup>PP</sup>\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|9\n|-align=center\n|align=left|'''[[Roman Vlasov]]'''\n|align=left|[[Wrestling at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's Greco-Roman 75 kg|\u221275 kg]]\n|{{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Kim Hyeon-woo|Kim H-w]]|KOR|2016 Summer}}<br />'''W''' 3\u20131 <sup>PP</sup>\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Yang Bin (wrestler)|Yang B]]|CHN|2016 Summer}}<br />'''W''' 4\u20130 <sup>ST</sup>\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Bo\u017eo Star\u010devi\u0107|Star\u010devi\u0107]]|CRO|2016 Summer}}<br/> '''W''' 3\u20131 <sup>PP</sup>\n|colspan=2 {{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Mark Madsen (wrestler)|Madsen]]|DEN|2016 Summer}}<br/> '''W''' 3\u20131 <sup>PP</sup>\n|{{gold01}}\n|-align=center\n|align=left|'''[[Davit Chakvetadze]]'''\n|align=left|[[Wrestling at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's Greco-Roman 85 kg|\u221285 kg]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Saman Tahmasebi|Tahmasebi]]|AZE|2016 Summer}}<br/> '''W''' 3\u20130 <sup>PO</sup>\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Habibollah Akhlaghi|Akhlaghi]]|IRI|2016 Summer}}<br/> '''W''' 5\u20130 <sup>VT</sup>\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Denis Kudla (wrestler)|Kudla]]|GER|2016 Summer}}<br/> '''W''' 4\u20130 <sup>ST</sup>\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Viktor L\u0151rincz|L\u0151rincz]]|HUN|2016 Summer}}<br/> '''W''' 3\u20131 <sup>ST</sup>\n|colspan=2 {{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Zhan Beleniuk|Beleniuk]]|UKR|2016 Summer}}<br />'''W''' 3\u20131 <sup>PP</sup>\n|{{gold01}}\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Islam Magomedov]]\n|align=left|[[Wrestling at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's Greco-Roman 98 kg|\u221298 kg]]\n|{{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Ardo Arusaar|Arusaar]]|EST|2016 Summer}}<br/> '''W''' 3\u20130 <sup>PO</sup>\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Cenk \u0130ldem|\u0130ldem]]|TUR|2016 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 1\u20133 <sup>PP</sup>\n|colspan=4|Did not advance\n|8\n|-align=center\n|align=left|'''[[Sergey Semenov (wrestler)|Sergey Semenov]]'''\n|align=left|[[Wrestling at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's Greco-Roman 130 kg|\u2212130 kg]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Murat Ramonov|Ramonov]]|KGZ|2016 Summer}}<br/> '''W''' 3\u20131 <sup>PP</sup>\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Muminjon Abdullaev|Abdullaev]]|UZB|2016 Summer}}