lev]]\n|align=left rowspan=2|[[Fencing at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's sabre|Sabre]]\n|{{n/a}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Tam\u00e1s Decsi|Decsi]]|HUN|2016 Summer}}<br>'''W''' 15\u201310\n||{{flagIOCathlete|[[Aldo Montano (fencer born 1978)|Montano]]|ITA|2016 Summer}}<br>'''W''' 15\u201313\n||{{flagIOCathlete|[[Kim Jung-hwan (fencer)|Kim J-h]]|KOR|2016 Summer}}<br>'''L''' 10\u201315\n|colspan=3|Did not advance\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Aleksey Yakimenko]]\n|{{n/a}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Pancho Paskov|Paskov]]|BUL|2016 Summer}}<br>'''L''' 14\u201315\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|}\n\n;Women\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n!rowspan=2|Athlete\n!rowspan=2|Event\n!Round of 64\n!Round of 32\n!Round of 16\n!Quarterfinal\n!Semifinal\n!colspan=2|Final / {{abbr|BM|Bronze medal match}}\n|- style=\"font-size:95%\"\n!Opposition<br>Score\n!Opposition<br>Score\n!Opposition<br>Score\n!Opposition<br>Score\n!Opposition<br>Score\n!Opposition<br>Score\n!Rank\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Violetta Kolobova]]\n|align=left rowspan=3|[[Fencing at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's \u00e9p\u00e9e|\u00c9p\u00e9e]]\n|{{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Choi In-jeong|Choi I-j]]|KOR|2016 Summer}}<br>'''L''' 12\u201315\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Tatiana Logunova]]\n|{{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Nozomi Nakano|Nakano]]|JPN|2016 Summer}}<br>'''L''' 14\u201315\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Lyubov Shutova]]\n|{{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Vivian Kong|Kong]]|HKG|2016 Summer}}<br>'''L''' 10\u201315\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|- align=center\n|align=left|'''[[Violetta Kolobova]]<br>[[Tatiana Logunova]]<br>[[Lyubov Shutova]]<br/>[[Olga Kochneva]]'''\n|align=left|[[Fencing at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's team \u00e9p\u00e9e|Team \u00e9p\u00e9e]]\n|colspan=2 {{n/a}}\n|{{n/a|Bye}}\n|{{flagIOCteam|FRA|2016 Summer}}<br>'''W''' 44\u201341\n|{{flagIOCteam|ROU|2016 Summer}}<br>'''L''' 31\u201345\n|{{flagIO